  "2026-03-07T22:44:57.400Z",maintainer-agent,Initial pm test run exposed Commander alias limitations when three long flags were declared on one option. Reworked create/update alias registration to separate --estimated_minutes options and retained required create validation in normalizeCreateOptions.
